#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.121"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.121:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:0.2"
msgid "12. Dhammakathikavagga "
msgstr "12. A Dhamma speaker "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 121. Upādāniyasutta → upādānam (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.121:0.3"
msgid "121. Upādāniyasutta "
msgstr "121. Things Prone To Being Grasped "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.2"
msgid "“Upādāniye ca, bhikkhave, dhamme desessāmi upādānañca. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you the things that are prone to being grasped, and the grasping. "

msgctxt "sn22.121:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha. "
msgstr "Listen … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.4"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, upādāniyā dhammā, katamaṃ upādānaṃ? "
msgstr "What are the things that are prone to being grasped? And what is the grasping? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.5"
msgid "Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, upādāniyo dhammo, "
msgstr "Form is something that’s prone to being grasped. "

msgctxt "sn22.121:1.6"
msgid "yo tattha chandarāgo, taṃ tattha upādānaṃ. "
msgstr "The desire and greed for it is the grasping. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.7"
msgid "Vedanā … pe … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.8"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.9"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.10"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ upādāniyo dhammo; "
msgstr "Consciousness is something that’s prone to being grasped. "

msgctxt "sn22.121:1.11"
msgid "yo tattha chandarāgo, taṃ tattha upādānaṃ. "
msgstr "The desire and greed for it is the grasping. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.12"
msgid "Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, upādāniyā dhammā, idaṃ upādānan”ti. "
msgstr "These are called the things that are prone to being grasped, and this is the grasping.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.121:1.13"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

